4
00:00:23,800 --> 00:00:24,480
Therefore,

5
00:00:25,040 --> 00:00:27,640
it's best for a woman to ask the way at the grave.

6
00:00:27,840 --> 00:00:28,600
Wanrong,

7
00:00:29,240 --> 00:00:30,000
Yinlian,

8
00:00:36,360 --> 00:00:38,000
