9
00:00:38,960 --> 00:00:39,760
would be best.

10
00:00:49,040 --> 00:00:50,320
Using the living

11
00:00:50,760 --> 00:00:52,360
to ask the way to the underworld.

12
00:00:52,360 --> 00:00:53,360
What do you seek?

13
00:00:53,760 --> 00:00:54,690
Tell me quickly.

14
00:01:15,320 --> 00:01:16,120
Slap the face.

15
00:01:21,800 --> 00:01:22,360
Why

16
00:01:22,800 --> 00:01:23,200
are you

17
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:24,280
