21
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:38,759
Hurry up.

22
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:47,970
Do not play tricks in front of spirits.

23
00:01:50,360 --> 00:01:51,039
What are you doing?

24
00:01:51,039 --> 00:01:51,400
Me?

25
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:52,479
It wasn't me.

26
00:01:58,240 --> 00:01:59,770
Together in life and death.

27
