34
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:20,680
You beast!

35
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,960
How dare you speak such nonsense!

36
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:23,760
She's coming.

37
00:02:30,079 --> 00:02:30,760
Going home.

38
00:02:31,640 --> 00:02:32,770
She wants to go home.

39
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:37,920
