42
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:47,130
Push harder!

43
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:51,520
Everyone, push harder!

44
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:52,560
It's just ahead.

45
00:02:58,079 --> 00:02:59,210
It's too late today.

46
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:00,520
We'll rest here.

47
00:03:02,160 --> 00:03:02,720
My Lord.

48
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:04,400
Have pity on me.

49
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:05,400
Have mercy.

50
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:07,080
Give me something to eat.

51
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:08,400
