56
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:21,970
There are many taboos on this journey.

57
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:24,720
Do not argue with anyone.

58
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:27,160
Do not drink alcohol.

59
00:03:28,440 --> 00:03:31,200
You must wait until the rooster crows before setting off.

60
00:03:31,200 --> 00:03:32,200
When it gets dark,

61
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:34,840
