64
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:44,000
It's not yet dawn.

65
00:03:44,200 --> 00:03:44,800
Hurry up.

66
00:03:45,040 --> 00:03:45,520
Hurry.

67
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,800
Hurry, hurry, hurry.

68
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:48,000
Hurry, hurry up.

69
00:03:53,320 --> 00:03:54,000
Hurry up.

70
00:03:54,640 --> 00:03:55,320
It's getting light.

71
00:03:55,320 --> 00:03:56,000
Okay, sir.

72
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:58,120
Push harder on your side.

73
00:03:58,120 --> 00:03:58,850
Push harder.

74
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:07,440
Push harder.

75
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:19,760
Are you

76
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:22,200
the ones who brought

77
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:23,680
