78
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:26,760
Who are you?

79
00:04:28,840 --> 00:04:30,040
I'm her father.

80
00:04:31,200 --> 00:04:31,920
Last night,

81
00:04:32,640 --> 00:04:34,880
Ruyan, who has been away for so many years

82
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:37,080
without any news,

83
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:38,120
suddenly

84
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:39,600
came to me in a dream

85
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,640
and told me she was coming

86
00:04:41,640 --> 00:04:42,600
