91
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:51,640
We...

92
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:53,000
We...

93
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:56,200
We were entrusted by someone

94
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:58,020
to bring her back to her roots.

95
00:04:58,640 --> 00:04:59,600
My condolences.

96
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:04,760
According to our village's rules,

97
00:05:05,400 --> 00:05:06,840
