99
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:11,800
It must be left at the village entrance.

100
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:13,800
You are Ruyan's friend.

101
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:15,760
Come with me.

102
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:18,840
Wait here.

103
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:20,760
Okay.

104
00:05:46,960 --> 00:05:48,360
Even the coffin is ready.

105
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:50,659
It seems that Ruyan's resentment

106
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:51,880
