120
00:06:15,840 --> 00:06:16,680
That's impossible.

121
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:17,320
He just...

122
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:27,640
Stay back.

123
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:48,200
Stay back.

124
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:49,400
Stay back.

125
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:51,000
Stay back.

126
00:06:54,880 --> 00:06:56,400
