129
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,440
My husband.

130
00:07:17,280 --> 00:07:18,810
It's time for the ceremony.

131
00:07:26,840 --> 00:07:29,970
First, bow to the underworld as the soul leaves the body.

132
00:07:30,400 --> 00:07:33,520
Second, enter the coffin to meet the deceased wife.

133
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:37,400
The ceremony is complete.

134
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:59,320
People fear three longs and two shorts.

135
00:07:59,320 --> 00:08:01,280
