136
00:08:01,280 --> 00:08:02,640
This is not a good sign.

137
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:04,700
He must have broken a taboo on the way.

138
00:08:05,080 --> 00:08:05,810
Master Wang.

139
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:06,320
I...

140
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:08,320
