141
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:09,520
Please do something!

142
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:12,200
Follow me.

143
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:13,120
Okay.

144
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:13,680
Okay.

145
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,560
