178
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:58,400
holding the red string.

179
00:09:58,400 --> 00:09:59,080
Remember.

180
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:01,260
If anything unusual happens,

181
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:02,970
I will pull you back.

182
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:05,130
Then doing this,

183
00:10:06,520 --> 00:10:07,840
