185
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:10,800
My son

186
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:12,740
hasn't been caught by a ghost.

187
00:10:13,400 --> 00:10:15,280
If you don't find him before dawn,

188
00:10:15,680 --> 00:10:16,600
your son

189
00:10:17,400 --> 00:10:19,080
